rows.label: qst200708_msg0002
rows.name:
You shouldn't get cocky just
because you won once-mau!

rows.label: qst200708_msg0003
rows.name: The match is far from over-mau!

rows.label: qst200708_msg0004
rows.name: It wasn't a single round match...?

rows.label: qst200708_msg0005
rows.name:
The next thing to steal is... the
Emperor Nefer's underwear-mau!!

rows.label: qst200708_msg0006
rows.name: Hah?! Underwear as in that underwear?

rows.label: qst200708_msg0008
rows.name:
There's no joy in stealing
something like that, mo?

rows.label: qst200708_msg0009
rows.name:
Don't underestimate it
as just underwear-mau!

rows.label: qst200708_msg0010
rows.name:
It might seem like a
trivial thing, but...

rows.label: qst200708_msg0011
rows.name:
If you get caught, you could be in
jail for life... or at worst,
executed-mau! It's a dangerous match-mau!

rows.label: qst200708_msg0012
rows.name:
Do you have the resolve to accept
this high-risk challenge-mau?!

rows.label: qst200708_msg0013
rows.name:
High-risk sounds delicious, so
I'd like to try eating it-ppo!

rows.label: qst200708_msg0015
rows.name:
Idaten seems to be
misunderstanding something, mo...

rows.label: qst200708_msg0016
rows.name:
Now, now! Let's begin
the second round-mau!

rows.label: qst200708_msg0017
rows.name:
Once you've stolen Emperor
Nefer's underwear, we'll meet
at Nharil Central Plaza-mau!
